Class TokenPair

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.susx.mlcl.byblo.io.TokenPair
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<TokenPair>
public final class TokenPair
extends Object
implements Comparable<TokenPair>, Serializable, Cloneable

TokenPair holds the unique ids of two indexed strings.

Instances of TokenPair are immutable.

Author:
Hamish I A Morgan <hamish.morgan@sussex.ac.uk>
